org.sakaiproject.entity.api

Interface ResourceProperties

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ResourcePropertiesEdit
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseResourceProperties, BaseResourcePropertiesEdit, ResourcePropertiesEditStub

    public interface ResourceProperties
extends Serializable

    ResourceProperties models the open-ended propeties of a Sakai Entity.

        stack - The DOM elements, the top of which is the containing element of the new "resource" element.
        Returns:
        The newly added element.
